{"tid":32592,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳 業 坤 搵 到 錢 秘 密 開 西 裝 舖","createTime":"2016-12-10T09:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T05:21:13.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89c9064bdd75ee46bf20280e905ab7d54f1ddfbf","tid":32592,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:12:19.000Z","msg":"「屋邨新人王」吳業坤（坤坤）一直以來形象夠貼地，所以深受大眾喜愛。捱足5年的他今年初終於成功彈起，演出、廣告代言等工作接踵而來，身價暴升不少，為他帶來豐厚進帳。不過屋邨出身的他未有因此而變成大花筒，反而貫徹低調作風，繼續在人前扮窮，更暗地裏將所賺到的錢用來投資副業，實行錢搵錢！<br />\n<br />\n黃千庭落舖揀戰衣<br />\n其實坤坤於2014年已初嘗做老闆的滋味，與同為「巨聲幫」的藝人陳國峰合資開設食肆「巨二拉麵」，而今次他選擇向服裝業發展，成為繼蘇志威及孫耀威後，再創立西裝店的藝人。坤坤好友兼創作歌手黃千庭接受電台訪問，提到要挑選戰衣出席樂壇頒獎禮時，就大爆坤坤近日開設西裝店：「近排佢開咗間西裝店，佢都有叫我去睇。」<br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀插旗試業中<br />\n記者聯絡坤坤查詢時，秘密再次榮升老闆的他明顯不欲透露太多，只表示投資的西裝店位於尖沙咀的百利商場，他說：「暫時係試業中，好快會開業，遲啲再講，到時會再邀請大家。」百利商場入面有眾多與婚慶有關的商戶，而坤坤的西裝店在地庫層的當眼位置。若果坤坤親自做生招牌的話，相信以其人氣定能招徠不少生意！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20161209/photo/bkn-20161209232354474-1209_00862_001_01p.jpg?20161210145419\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20161209%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161209232354474-1209_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20161210145419&h=d19c15ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acf528e2986326ebe3b77cfed8ada664127ac045","tid":32592,"uid":22431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:13:52.000Z","msg":"坤坤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccdcfae7658d39ef1f5e2903925218a7e14c8c74","tid":32592,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:14:06.000Z","msg":"傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d19e0b42515d8e64890dac1a891ab418492ba83","tid":32592,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:14:29.000Z","msg":"等破產啦"},{"pid":"02e13a57f565bf33fe90973d5438dce0d4117731","tid":32592,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:14:42.000Z","msg":"好醒目"},{"pid":"961b7b724b42c59d188a78129370104da2a916da","tid":32592,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:23:07.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾 <br />\n祝債台高築 早日破產"},{"pid":"4f49472cc7bcfe18d4d219b1620d80d82bac5664","tid":32592,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:23:54.000Z","msg":"希望早日收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c7f5f351aa2f4d3e14cf89fc3d669bb2da7eba","tid":32592,"uid":60092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:26:19.000Z","msg":"餐廳名都開埋，係時候去做打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e7a3e7430ef620daaf5c81f768e50a038378a4c","tid":32592,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:26:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3df68265a34e42ec085624a3fdbcf88e2db1efb","tid":32592,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:28:08.000Z","msg":"以佢依家個人氣認為仲做到生招牌咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4778b1bec253cd1ab8b2bf5c24df448dde73fa33","tid":32592,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:51:33.000Z","msg":"賣棋就話做到生招牌啫"},{"pid":"a55c3dc30efe480bfd3252a54320319f82832ab2","tid":32592,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T06:31:21.000Z","msg":"爆完自己間鋪名做宣傳仲係秘密？"},{"pid":"4c79d6017c85da5c1e93b5158b1cb205a9c05164","tid":32592,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T06:33:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cdf2ecbf87bb390f75b58ac8a01fc5a6820eac2c","tid":32592,"uid":16239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T06:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賣棋就話做到生招牌啫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係囉，解議佢開間棋鋪"},{"pid":"5d23a3b355422856ac95bae7ab0e15df4a121fe4","tid":32592,"uid":